{"tid":797960,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩連奴慘負熱刺後，竟反獲加薪5%","createTime":"2018-08-29T02:39:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T16:39:44.000Z","uid":1426,"like":18,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c1d826e6d282c1de3003ab90e7c6d086a2800592","tid":797960,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T02:39:45.000Z","msg":"新巴城巴加薪5%　追溯到今年1月<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/201804/31682524_10156248576674330_3244568378735591424_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F201804%2F31682524_10156248576674330_3244568378735591424_n.jpg&h=2e59563f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新巴城巴今日（8月28日）分別與汽車交通運輸業總工會新巴分會、新巴職工會、城巴勞資協商會、汽車交通運輸業總工會城巴分會及城巴職工會達成共識，2018年度加薪5%，全職車長及全職前線員工的最低加薪金額為$1,100，加薪生效日期會追溯至今年1月1日。 以一名新入職車長的薪金計算，其底薪的加幅為7.2%。今次加薪連同本年3月起生效的薪酬架構調整方案，以每日工作10小時計算，車長薪酬比去年上升了15.2%。加上年度特別獎金，新入職車長的每月平均收入為$22,986元。 新巴城巴同時會於9月1日起提升員工福利，包括全職車長及技工職級員工，將增設3個增薪點，於每年公司指定之12個工作天當值，於該指定日之超時津貼以時薪2倍計算。 <br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/08-28-2018/47786\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F08-28-2018%2F47786&d=%2F7PvxGVesDDcZSZb%2Fw0Ahb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=df42f01d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/08-28-2018/47786</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2018"},{"pid":"a43c092a3aa706c4caeb522ab5ab24011859910b","tid":797960,"uid":124616,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T02:40:52.000Z","msg":"好撚好笑呀"},{"pid":"2383b4f9f4e3cb8e6b50de384b691cdad4ad7466","tid":797960,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T02:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2d0960765610b20d385b321cbf9f6659daef651","tid":797960,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T02:41:55.000Z","msg":"熱狗係咁上下"},{"pid":"aa874